professor of the Chinese University of Political Sciences and Law,
also serves as arbitrator of Stockholm International Arbitration
Court and for other international organizations.
</P>
<P>
He is credited with handling many cases and avoiding billions
of dollars of losses for the State, including one attempted fraud
involving 10 billion US dollars against a Chinese state-owned bank.
</P>
