opportunities and boost the incomes of Kenyan people. The products
will be exported to surrounding countries after satisfying local
needs.
</P>
<P>
Godana said that China's assistance to Kenya involving economic,
medical and cultural fields has played an important role in the
economic development of the country.
</P>
