<HEADLINE> DRC to Hold Multi-Party Debate in Kenya </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 28 (Xinhua) -- The government of the Democratic
Republic of Congo (DRC) announced here Tuesday that a national
multi-party debate for Congolese politicians will be held in the
Kenyan capital Nairobi from May 8 to 15.
</P>
