Dini warned Tuesday that NATO will risk damaging its credibility
as a force for stability if air strikes against Yugoslavia last
too long.
</P>
<P>
In an interview published Wednesday by Italian daily Il Foglio,
Dini said, "NATO must safeguard its credibility as a force for
stability."
</P>
