<HEADLINE> Two Seeds Advance in Hamburg </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Dominique van Roost and Nathalie
Tauziat, the two seeded players in action on Tuesday, advanced in
